},
"Factors to Consider When Prescribing Drugs to Treat Insomnia"
]
}
]
},
{
"type":"tag",
"tagName":"tbody",
"attrs":{
},
"children":[
{
"type":"tag",
"tagName":"tr",
"attrs":{
"className":"group_1-1 row-odd"
},
"children":[
{
"type":"tag",
"tagName":"td",
"attrs":{
"rowSpan":"1",
"colSpan":"1"
},
"children":[
" ",
{
"type":"p",
"hlId":"cd2b9c",
"class":"cell txt l",
"children":[
"Use the minimal effective dosage"
]
},
" "
]
}
]
},
{
"type":"tag",
"tagName":"tr",
"attrs":{
"className":"group_1-2 row-even"
},
"children":[
{
"type":"tag",
"tagName":"td",
"attrs":{
"rowSpan":"1",
"colSpan":"1"
},
"children":[
" ",
{
"type":"p",
"hlId":"7f38ad",
"class":"cell txt l",
"children":[
"Avoid long–half-life medications, including long–half-life metabolites"
]
},
" "
]
}
]
},
{
"type":"tag",
"tagName":"tr",
"attrs":{
"className":"group_1-3 row-odd"
},
"children":[
{
"type":"tag",
"tagName":"td",
"attrs":{
"rowSpan":"1",
"colSpan":"1"
},
"children":[
" ",
{
"type":"p",
"hlId":"68c0d7",
"class":"cell txt l",
"children":[
"Be aware of potential interactions between drugs, including over-the-counter drugs"
]
},
" "
]
}
]
},
{
"type":"tag",
"tagName":"tr",
"attrs":{
"className":"group_1-4 row-even"
},
"children":[
{
"type":"tag",
"tagName":"td",
"attrs":{
"rowSpan":"1",
"colSpan":"1"
},
"children":[
" ",
{
"type":"p",
"hlId":"62f0bb",
"class":"cell txt l",
"children":[
"Caution patients who are receiving these medications about interaction with alcohol"
]
},
" "
]
}
]
},
{
"type":"tag",
"tagName":"tr",
"attrs":{
"className":"group_1-5 row-odd"
},
"children":[
{
"type":"tag",
"tagName":"td",
"attrs":{
"rowSpan":"1",
"colSpan":"1"
},
"children":[
" ",
{
"type":"p",
"hlId":"55cc9f",
"class":"cell txt l",
"children":[
"Review potential side effects: daytime sleepiness, complex sleep behaviors, serious injury, or death"
]
},
" "
]
}
]
},
{
"type":"tag",
"tagName":"tr",
"attrs":{
"className":"group_1-6 row-even"
},
"children":[
{
"type":"tag",
"tagName":"td",
"attrs":{
"rowSpan":"1",
"colSpan":"1"
},
"children":[
" ",
{
"type":"p",
"hlId":"a35c2f",
"class":"cell txt l",
"children":[
"Confer with the patient to determine an appropriate period of use"
]
},
" "
]
}
]
},
{
"type":"tag",
"tagName":"tr",
"attrs":{
"className":"group_1-7 row-odd"
},
"children":[
{
"type":"tag",
"tagName":"td",
"attrs":{
"rowSpan":"1",
"colSpan":"1"
},
"children":[
" ",
{
"type":"p",
"hlId":"4e6c9f",
"class":"cell txt l",
"children":[
"Use a γ-aminobutyric acid agonist before other sedative-hypnotics for treatment of acute or short-term insomnia"
]
},
" "
]
}
]
},
{
"type":"tag",
"tagName":"tr",
"attrs":{
"className":"group_1-8 row-even"
},
"children":[
{
"type":"tag",
"tagName":"td",
"attrs":{
"rowSpan":"1",
"colSpan":"1"
},
"children":[
" ",
{
"type":"p",
"hlId":"4c3da0",
"class":"cell txt l",
"children":[
"Look for rebound insomnia after discontinuation"
]
},
" "
]
}
]
},
{
"type":"tag",
"tagName":"tr",
"attrs":{
"className":"group_1-9 row-odd"
},
"children":[
{
"type":"tag",
"tagName":"td",
"attrs":{
"rowSpan":"1",
"colSpan":"1"
},
"children":[
" ",
{
"type":"p",
"hlId":"511616",
"class":"cell txt l",
"children":[
"Consider consulting a sleep specialist before starting long-term therapy with hypnotic medication"
]
},
" "
]
}
]
},
{
"type":"tag",
"tagName":"tr",
"attrs":{
"className":"group_1-10 row-even"
},
"children":[
{
"type":"tag",
"tagName":"td",
"attrs":{
"rowSpan":"1",
"colSpan":"1"
},
"children":[
" ",
{
"type":"p",
"hlId":"f55ca1",
"class":"cell txt l",
"children":[
"Consider intermittent or long-term use of hypnotic medications, depending on the clinical situation"
]
},
" "
]
}
]
}
]
}
]
